06:04.930 --> 06:07.372
Christ who strengthens me.

06:08.634 --> 06:09.214
Did you get that?

06:10.175 --> 06:11.176
I said, hey, do it again.

06:11.777 --> 06:17.402
And he goes, I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me.

06:17.522 --> 06:20.485
And I'm like, dude, that is awesome.

06:20.645 --> 06:21.646
He said, yes, it is.

06:21.787 --> 06:22.407
Just remember.

06:22.868 --> 06:23.588
And he walked by.

06:26.992 --> 06:33.458
In our life, part of our responsibility is to find words that stick

06:33.538 --> 06:37.003
words that are in line with what God wants us to be.

06:37.043 --> 06:41.270
And we have a manual in case you didn't know.

06:42.592 --> 06:48.762
And nestle within that manual are those words that frame and shape how God wants us to live.

06:49.062 --> 06:51.506
It is literally what we call the word of God.

06:52.770 --> 06:58.437
And so as we read it and study it, we as the church have tried to build spaces for you to find that.

06:58.537 --> 06:59.498
Andy does devotion.

06:59.518 --> 07:00.439
You can find online.

07:00.459 --> 07:01.741
There are Sunday school classes.

07:02.061 --> 07:03.623
