07:03.944 --> 07:11.152
There's the worship service where we try to take the word and put it in your heart and sew it into your life.

07:12.434 --> 07:17.300
And so when you want to be salt and light, the word salt and light have to be in you.

07:19.723 --> 07:22.546
And you have to learn it.

07:24.162 --> 07:26.284
Your praise team comes in practices.

07:26.705 --> 07:29.147
