07:32.811 --> 07:34.953
What if they didn't blend their music together?

07:35.894 --> 07:38.797
What if they didn't know what they were singing?

07:41.720 --> 07:52.050
As a preacher, one of the things that's really frustrated me is I think somehow people in the pews think they absorb the word by osmosis through their behind in a pew.

07:53.922 --> 07:55.123
