08:39.427 --> 08:45.395
The man who was their pastor was old like me and he kind of stumbled around and he wasn't real eloquent.

08:45.936 --> 08:48.800
And so they were so excited to have this young man's energy.

08:49.140 --> 08:53.106
And so he came in and as he started his speech,

08:53.794 --> 09:04.591
He read so eloquently the 23rd Psalm and the congregation was just like melting like butter at every word he would say and read.

09:05.793 --> 09:10.640
