10:07.255 --> 10:15.026
My mother-in-law, this too shall past, didn't shape me because of the words that shape me because she lived that.

10:15.714 --> 10:16.775
She was that.

10:17.796 --> 10:18.838
She taught us that.

10:20.320 --> 10:39.122
Part of the responsibility, if you go back and look at our scripture text, is that Jesus calls us through Paul, not only to know the word, but to learn it together in community and to hold each other accountable in it.

10:40.194 --> 10:58.834
I'm just going to tell you, if you're not in some group of learning, if you're not in a process of bringing the Word into you and growing into your relationship with Christ, that Word is not going to be what it was meant to be the living Word that lives inside of you, that comes to life.

10:59.138 --> 11:01.000
that forms and shapes you.

11:01.261 --> 11:03.844
In this world, people use the Scripture loosely.

11:04.185 --> 11:05.927
Lynn Sweet calls it Versitis.

11:06.007 --> 11:09.832
People pull out a verse in the Bible and use it to justify whatever they do.

11:10.153 --> 11:11.975
