11:13.477 --> 11:17.622
Jesus said, I've come that you might have life.

11:18.023 --> 11:20.807
I'm not going to tell you you're wrong if you say the wrong thing.

11:21.428 --> 11:26.354
I've come that you might have life and have it abundantly.

11:26.786 --> 11:32.695
The Word is given to us, not that we're going to get to heaven and have an essay question.

11:34.678 --> 11:42.650
The Word was given to us that we would learn and have the life Jesus and God and the Holy Spirit have intended us to have since creation.

11:44.633 --> 11:46.256
So being in the Word is not enough.

11:47.477 --> 11:48.900
The Word has to be in you.

11:51.123 --> 11:53.106
The Word has to be in you.

11:53.986 --> 11:55.588
And that word is a living word.

11:55.648 --> 11:56.810
It is God Himself.

11:57.191 --> 12:01.116
Jesus was the incarnation of the Word of God.

12:01.216 --> 12:05.743
The Word become flesh and dwelling in and among us.

12:06.944 --> 12:10.149
And so what are you doing to nurture that relationship?

