For days, Mary and Joseph look for Jesus and where did they find him?

12:29.024 --> 12:41.739
At the foot of the scholars and the rabbis, asking them questions, finding the word so many times we think of Jesus as only divine, but he was fully human and he was learning and finding his words.

12:42.740 --> 12:54.194
And those words that he learned as a child from his father, those words that he learned from those rabbis, those words that he learned from going to synagogue and being a part of a worshiping community framed

12:54.434 --> 12:56.236
and strengthened his ministry.

