14:22.626 --> 14:27.696
They don't belong to this world just as I don't belong to this world.

14:29.139 --> 14:31.083
Sanctify them in the truth.

14:32.686 --> 14:34.871
Your word is truth.

14:39.260 --> 14:41.845
Jesus took the words that formed and shaped them.

14:42.266 --> 14:44.370
And then in relationship with God,

14:44.482 --> 14:53.891
invited us to be a part of that word and to be in a word world that doesn't know that word, which takes us to the last part of becoming salt and light.

14:54.191 --> 14:59.917
You don't just need to know the word and the one, you need to know the way to live that out.

15:01.798 --> 15:06.343
How do you become the word, the salt and the light for this world?

15:06.743 --> 15:11.227
How do you find your way into letting those thoughts form and shape you?

15:11.588 --> 15:14.130
I have to tell you, you remember the rule of 10?

15:17.986 --> 15:26.094
Four years after that young man had told me about the rule of 10, I had open heart surgery, quadruple bypass, six blockages.

15:27.295 --> 15:29.817
I couldn't preach for three months.

15:30.958 --> 15:35.102
I was at home in depression, pouting, mad at God.

15:37.805 --> 15:41.468
And the Holy Spirit put those words on my heart.

15:41.488 --> 15:46.033
I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me.

15:46.693 --> 15:47.474
A little boy.

15:49.538 --> 15:53.404
And I began to marinate in that as I started physical therapy, I had a trainer.

15:53.985 --> 15:57.209
And in our second time together, I was trying to duck walk.

15:57.249 --> 16:04.260
If y'all ever duck walked as an exercise, that's cruel and unusual punishment, especially if you don't have a strong core.

16:04.280 --> 16:09.848
Cause I would get about two little waddles and then I'd fall over like a weebel and just kind of go to my side.

16:09.888 --> 16:11.551
Y'all probably don't even know what a weebel is.

16:11.631 --> 16:13.714
So I probably shouldn't have used that.

16:14.434 --> 16:26.030
And I was just, I was mad at myself and my trainer came over and he helped me up and he patted me on the back and he said, bro, Steve, your problem is your core is weak.

16:26.050 --> 16:27.031
I was like, excuse me.

16:29.354 --> 16:29.915
Excuse me.

16:31.116 --> 16:31.998
Your core is weak.

16:33.019 --> 16:34.441
He said, we're going to work on your core.

16:37.024 --> 16:38.466
Week after week, he would do that.

16:38.486 --> 16:44.274
And I began to see my body get stronger and the Holy Spirit started working to me and was saying core.

16:46.978 --> 16:48.260
My faith was weak too.

16:50.903 --> 16:52.905
I was wobbling through the hardest of times.

16:54.647 --> 17:05.841
And I began to think about that word and I created an acrostic that now I'm working on and I use in my training called core strength, centered, ordered, related and engaged.

17:07.523 --> 17:10.507
The word has become flesh in me.

17:14.011 --> 17:16.594
That's the gift God seeks to give all of us.

17:16.802 --> 17:18.364
