17:22.389 --> 17:28.656
Your life verse may not be the same life verse, but what's really incredible is if we all put our life verses together, guess what?

17:30.058 --> 17:31.620
We really get the living word.

17:32.982 --> 17:35.084
Today we're celebrating communion.

17:38.128 --> 17:43.154
Sometimes we forget about the word that formed and shaped that for Jesus.

17:44.898 --> 17:47.381
he had set the room for the Passover meal.

