18:30.466 --> 18:35.454
My God, my God, why have you forsaken me?

18:36.856 --> 18:43.186
In Psalms 19, he writes, your word is a lamp unto my path and a light unto my feet.

18:44.034 --> 18:53.426
That word in that moment, what we don't understand about that word is that word came from a Psalm that was beginning as a word of despair.

18:53.446 --> 18:57.211
